            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="box">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <hr>
                <h2 class="intro-text text-center">
                    Beautiful boxes
                    <strong>to showcase your content</strong>
                </h2>
                <hr>
                <p>Use as many boxes as you like, and put anything you want in them! They are great for just about anything, the sky's the limit!</p>
